<inglise> Having regard to the Act of Accession of Greece, and in particular paragraph 9 of Protocol 4 on cotton, as last amended by Regulation (EC) No 1553/95 (1), </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Kreeka &uuml;hinemisakti, eriti puuvilla k&auml;sitleva protokolli nr 4 (viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 1553/95 (1)) l&otilde;iget 9, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the proposal by the Commission (2), </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse komisjoni ettepanekut (2) </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Protocol 4 of the Act of Accession of Greece and Council Regulation (EEC) No 1964/87 of 2 July 1987 adjusting the system of aid for cotton introduced by Protocol 4 annexed to the Act of Accession of Greece (3) have been amended by Regulation (EC) No 1553/95; whereas Council Regulation (EEC) No 2169/81 of 27 July 1981 laying down the general rules for the system of aid for cotton (4) should accordingly be amended; whereas the significance of the adjustments that need to be made to Regulation (EEC) No 2169/81 and the large number of amendments already made to it make it appropriate to recast this Regulation for the purposes of clarity and transparence; whereas Regulation (EEC) No 2169/81 should therefore be repealed; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: Kreeka &uuml;hinemisakti protokolli nr 4 ja n&otilde;ukogu 2. juuli 1987. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 1964/87, millega kohandatakse Kreeka &uuml;hinemisaktile lisatud protokolliga nr 4 kehtestatud puuvilla abis&uuml;steemi, (3) on muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 1553/95; sellest tulenevalt tuleks muuta n&otilde;ukogu 27. juuli 1981. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 2169/81, milles s&auml;testatakse puuvilla abis&uuml;steemi &uuml;ldeeskirjad; (4) m&auml;&auml;rusesse (EM&Uuml;) nr 2169/81 tehtavate muudatuste olulisuse ja juba tehtud muudatuste suure arvu t&otilde;ttu on asjakohane selguse ja l&auml;bipaistvuse huvides v&otilde;tta vastu k&otilde;nealuse m&auml;&auml;ruse uus redaktsioon; seep&auml;rast tuleks m&auml;&auml;rus (EM&Uuml;) nr 2169/81 kehtetuks tunnistada; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, pursuant to paragraph 9 of the Protocol, it is necessary to lay down the rules of procedure and sound management for its application, the general rules of the system of production aid, the criteria for determining the world market price and the rules concerning the financing of the measures envisaged; </inglise>
<eesti> k&otilde;nealuse protokolli l&otilde;ike 9 kohaselt on vaja s&auml;testada menetlust ja korrektset juhtimist k&auml;sitlevad eeskirjad k&otilde;nealuse protokolli kohaldamiseks, tootmistoetuste s&uuml;steemi &uuml;ldeeskirjad, maailmaturuhinna kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ramise kriteeriumid ja kavandatud meetmete rahastamist k&auml;sitlevad eeskirjad; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, in order to facilitate the management and control of the aid system, provision should be made for a procedure establishing close cooperation between the Member States and the Commission within a Management Committee; whereas it is advisable to use the Management Committee for Flax and Hemp as provided for in Council Regulation (EEC) No 1308/70 of 29 June 1970 on the common organization of the market in flax and hemp (5); </inglise>
<eesti> abis&uuml;steemi haldamise ja kontrollimise h&otilde;lbustamiseks tuleks s&auml;testada kord, mille abil seatakse korralduskomitee raames sisse tihe koost&ouml;&ouml; liikmesriikide ja komisjoni vahel; on soovitatav toetuda n&otilde;ukogu 29. juuni 1970. aasta m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 1308/70 (lina- ja kanepituru &uuml;hise korralduse kohta) (5) etten&auml;htud lina- ja kanepituru korralduskomitee abile; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, in accordance with Article 2 of Regulation (EEC) No 1964/87, the aid shall be altered by adjustments yet to be determined where the Community production exceeds a quantity fixed in advance; whereas, in consequence, the amount of aid to be granted cannot be determined until the actual quantity produced is itself known; whereas, to offset the adverse effects of late payment of aid for the parties involved, provision should be made for the part of the aid to be paid in advance; </inglise>
<eesti> vastavalt m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1964/87 artiklile 2 muudetakse abi alles kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ratavate kohandustega, kui &uuml;henduse toodang &uuml;letab eelnevalt kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ratud kogust; sellest tulenevalt ei saa antava abi summat kindlaks m&auml;&auml;rata enne tegelikult toodetud koguse teadasaamist; abi hilisest maksmisest asjaomastele pooltele tulenevate kahjulike m&otilde;jude h&uuml;vitamiseks tuleks s&auml;testada, et osa abist makstakse ettemaksena; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, pursuant to the third subparagraph of paragraph 3 of the Protocol, the aid is determined on the basis of the difference between a guide price for unginned cotton and the world market price; whereas, since there is no international trade in unginned cotton, and there are therefore no offers or quotations, provision should be made to enable a world market price for this product to be determined; whereas this price may be established on the basis of the historical relationship between the price agreed for ginned cotton and that calculated for unginned cotton; </inglise>
<eesti> protokolli l&otilde;ike 3 kolmanda l&otilde;igu kohaselt m&auml;&auml;ratakse abi kindlaks toorpuuvilla soovitushinna ja maailmaturuhinna erinevuse p&otilde;hjal; kuna toorpuuvilla puhul ei ole rahvusvahelist kaubandust ja seep&auml;rast puuduvad ka pakkumised v&otilde;i noteeringud, tuleks ette n&auml;ha s&auml;tted, et v&otilde;imaldada m&auml;&auml;rata k&otilde;nealuse toote maailmaturuhind; k&otilde;nealuse hinna v&otilde;ib kehtestada puuvillakiu kokkulepitud hinna ja toorpuuvilla arvutatud hinna vahelise varasema suhte p&otilde;hjal; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, when calculating the price of ginned cotton, account should be taken of the offers made on the world market and of the quotations on those exchanges that are important for international trade; whereas the price on the world market must be calculated using the most favourable offers and quotations on that market among those that are considered representative of the real market trend; </inglise>
<eesti> puuvillakiu hinna arvutamisel tuleks arvesse v&otilde;tta maailmaturul tehtud pakkumisi ja noteeringuid rahvusvahelises kaubanduses olulistel b&ouml;rsidel; maailmaturuhind tuleb arvutada, kasutades k&otilde;ige soodsamaid pakkumisi ja noteeringuid k&otilde;nealusel turul nende pakkumiste ja noteeringute hulgast, mida k&auml;sitatakse tegelikku turusuundumust esindavatena; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, for the aid system to operate correctly, the world market price must be recorded for a Community frontier crossing point; whereas, in fixing this point, account should be taken of the extent to which it is representative for imports of the products in question; whereas, therefore, in the case of multiple origins the ports of Northern Europe should be chosen and in the case of a limited number of origins, offers or quotations recorded on an exchange outside Europe the port of Piraeus should be chosen, whereas, in the latter case the offers and quotations adopted will need to be adjusted if they relate to some other frontier crossing point; </inglise>
<eesti> abis&uuml;steemi n&otilde;uetekohaseks toimimiseks tuleb maailmaturuhind registreerida &uuml;henduse piiri&uuml;letuspunkti jaoks; k&otilde;nealuse punkti kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ramisel tuleks arvesse v&otilde;tta, mil m&auml;&auml;ral on k&otilde;nealune punkt t&uuml;&uuml;piline k&otilde;nealuste toodete importimisel; seep&auml;rast tuleks mitme p&auml;ritoluriigi puhul valida P&otilde;hja-Euroopa sadamad ning piiratud arvu p&auml;ritoluriikide ja v&auml;ljaspool Euroopat asuvatel b&ouml;rsidel registreeritud pakkumiste ja noteeringute puhul Pireuse sadam; viimati mainitud juhul tuleb arvessev&otilde;etavaid pakkumisi ja noteeringuid kohandada, kui need on seotud m&otilde;ne muu piiri&uuml;letuspunktiga; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas such adjustments should also be made to the offers and quotations adopted in order to compensate for any variation from the presentation and quality taken as a basis for fixing the guide price; </inglise>
<eesti> samuti tuleks kohandada pakkumisi ja noteeringuid, mida kasutatakse h&uuml;vitamaks mis tahes varieerumist soovitushinna kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ramisel aluseks v&otilde;etava esitusviisi ja kvaliteedi puhul; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the producer Member States should be required to set up the control arrangements necessary to ensure that the aid system operates correctly; </inglise>
