<inglise> Whereas, with a view to subjecting the Community expenditure on applying the planned measure to financial and monetary rules and appropriate procedures, Council Regulation (EEC) No 729/70 of 21 April 1970 on the financing of the common agricultural policy (1), should apply mutatis mutandis to the matters dealt with herein, as should the Regulations relating to the value of the unit of account and the exchange rates to be applied within the framework of the common agricultural policy; </inglise>
<eesti> pidades silmas kavandatud meetme kohaldamisega seotud &uuml;henduse kulutuste allutamist finants- ja rahaeeskirjadele ning asjakohastele menetlustele, tuleks n&otilde;ukogu 21. aprilli 1970. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 729/70 &uuml;hise p&otilde;llumajanduspoliitika rahastamise kohta (6) ning samuti &uuml;hise p&otilde;llumajanduspoliitika raames kohaldatavaid arvestus&uuml;hiku v&auml;&auml;rtust ja &uuml;mberarvestuskursse k&auml;sitlevaid m&auml;&auml;rusi kohaldada k&otilde;nealuses valdkonnas mutatis mutandis; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the provisions of this Regulation should apply as from the 1995/96 marketing year so that the adjustments to the system provided for in Regulation (EC) No 1553/95 may be implemented by that date; </inglise>
<eesti> k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;ruse s&auml;tteid tuleks kohaldada alates 1995/96. majandusaastast, et m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 1553/95 etten&auml;htud s&uuml;steemikohandusi v&otilde;iks k&otilde;nealuseks kuup&auml;evaks rakendada; </eesti>
